@startuml
actor Staff
participant "Social Compose UI" as UI
participant "Marketing Service" as MS
participant "Catalog Service" as CS
database "SESHOP DB" as DB

Staff -> UI: Create Instagram draft(product)
UI -> MS: generateDraft(productId)
MS -> CS: getProductMedia(productId)
CS --> MS: media + product metadata
MS -> DB: insert instagram_drafts(status=NEW)
DB --> MS: draftId
MS --> UI: showDraft(caption, hashtags, mediaOrder)

Staff -> UI: Save edited draft
UI -> MS: saveDraft(draftId, caption, mediaOrder)
MS -> DB: update instagram_drafts
DB --> MS: updated

MS -> DB: mark draft READY_FOR_REVIEW
MS --> UI: showReviewReady
@enduml
